snippet.title: continuum Mac System 6.0.8
snippet.description: This is the game Continuum, running on Mac OS 6.0.8. Sorry about the flickering, this was the best capture I could achieve from the real hardware and a digital camera. This game was made by the Wilson brothers, and was Freeware.
